         \### Variables for ConTeXt\n\
         \\n\
         \Pandoc uses these variables when [creating a PDF] with ConTeXt.\n\
         \\n\
         \`fontsize`\n\
         \:   font size for body text (e.g. `10pt`, `12pt`)\n\
